programmes.show_description: Heart Of Darkness. Nine series veterans try to survive the deadly jungles of Ecuador's Amazon basin for 40 days and 40 nights. Hit by injury and hunger, they're pushed to the edge. S2, Ep1
What Lies Beneath. The seven remaining survivalists enter week two of their brutal challenge in the Amazon. After two tap-outs in the first four days, their priority is to find food. S2, Ep2

Return To K-Town. Mike and Tay build a commemorative clock for the town of Kannapolis, North Carolina, before the crew heads back to salvage items left behind on the first trip. S9, Ep6
Carpenters Hall. The crew stays local and heads just down the street in Roanoke where they salvage a one-of-a-kind sign and pick through an old meeting hall. S9, Ep7
Mining On A Prayer. Kris must move fast in the face of a life-threatening incident. Vernon pushes a diver for a personal record, and Shawn deals with a crack in the ice. S10, Ep29
Legend Vs. Underdog. A massive blizzard is about to hit Nome, Alaska, and bring the mining season to an end. Zeke risks one last move, while Shawn hits a big jackpot. S10, Ep30
Jacqui and Andrew get trapped behind the line of a devastating bushfire. The Gold Devils are torn apart when a team member goes off on their own. S9, Ep8
Hunt Begins, The. Julia's first mission is a giant python in a living room. Then, she tries to catch a snake trapped in an air conditioning box. S1, Ep1
Down to the Wire. The King Crab Season comes down to the wire, as the struggling skippers battle to top off their quotas. Who will land a bumper haul in this end of season sprint? S5, Ep7
Payback Time. It's the start of the 2009 Crab Season, and things are looking up for our spectacular skippers. But will their dreams been shattered by a colossal rogue wave? S5, Ep8
Into The Storm. A dangerous storm threatens to shut down the operation just as Darrell and team discover gold ore in the remains of an old wreck. S2, Ep7
Africa's Cursed Lake Of Gold. Josh Gates journeys to the wilds of Namibia to embark on a treacherously deep dive in Lake Otjikoto for a long lost World War I treasure. S3, Ep11
Gold Rush Of The Atlantic. Josh has a fresh lead on a shipwreck from 1715 with a potentially massive treasure haul. He launches an expedition into Florida's Atlantic coast. S6, Ep4
Drowning. In Hawaii the Raneys attempt to save two homesteaders whose dream homestead lays a flash-flood zone. As the weather closes in, can they save the property from the water? S1, Ep9
Honey I Torched The Homestead. In Oregon, the Raneys are called in to help snowbound homesteaders. Exposed to local predators, they worry about the region's forest fires. S1, Ep10
Risky Business. Justin gambles thousands of dollars as he is struggling this season. Kelly is in desperate need for a big find underground and Aaron and Greg's claim might pay off. S2, Ep4
Hot Hot Hot. The Rookies' relationship is on the rocks as they battle their biggest claim yet. With two partners working at different speeds, there's a fight brewing. S2, Ep5
Beastmode. Superbowl fever hits The Cornelia Marie, an injured crewman creates jeopardy on the Wizard, the Cape Caution makes a near fatal error, and the Time Bandit loses a Captain. S11, Ep16
I'm The Captain. The polar ice descends, threatening the end of season. Sig attempts to offload his crab before saving his gear, and Casey shows Josh what it means to be a Captain. S11, Ep17
A High Steaks Build. The crew kicks off a new waterside build, but a surprise call from the homeowners could change everything. S15, Ep2
Put To The Test. Mark and the guys make the seven-hour trek to Dubois, Indiana, to salvage a cabin picked by the youngest member of the crew. S15, Ep2
Shane and Russell gamble on a unique wash plant. The Poseidon Crew search for an ancient river gutter, while Jacqui and Andrew battle intense heat. S6, Ep13
Outbreak. As they approach the halfway point of their brutal challenge, the remaining survivalists face a devastating setback when deadly bacteria threaten to take out their leader. S2, Ep4
Worlds Collide Part 2. After the loss of their chief provider, the remaining five survivalists endure yet another shocking development when they learn they are not alone in the Amazon. S2, Ep5

Roanoke Shopping Center. The team heads to a local shopping centre to salvage a large, decorative frame, rolling doors and more. They also find great items from a pick in New Jersey. S9, Ep8
Country Store And Gas Station. The crew salvages an old country store. Using materials from the project, Mike and Robert create a tribute bench for a veterans' retreat. S9, Ep9
The Empire Strikes Back - Part 1. Mining empires clash in the epic battle to dominate Nome. Mr. Gold has a plan to yield 3000 ounces, while the Kellys impress a new investor. S11, Ep1
The Empire Strikes Back - Part 2. Mining empires clash in the epic battle to dominate Nome. Mr. Gold has a plan to yield 3000 ounces, while the Kellys impress a new investor. S11, Ep2
Shane is lured out of retirement to find gold on Messenger's Patch. After pushing through a dust storm, Neville is called home for hospital tests. S9, Ep9
Land Of The Brown Snake, The. First up, Julia tackles two snakes in a crowded garage. Then, she deals with an eastern brown snake, the second most venomous snake in the world. S1, Ep2
No Second Chances. When the fleet arrives on the Opi grounds a skipper regrets sending his men out in savage weather to save the boat - there are no second chances on the Bering Sea. S5, Ep9
Sea Of Misery. Three weeks in, the miserable conditions already have the crabbers turning on each other. Plus deadly ice stands between one skipper and the safety of harbour. S5, Ep10
Striking Gold. Leading to one of the richest finds in Darrell's career, the team discovers ornate artefacts that indicate the location of a 16th century captain's quarters. S2, Ep8
True Cross Of Christ. Explorer Josh Gates journeys to Jerusalem and Istanbul searching for lost pieces of the cross from the crucifixion of Jesus Christ. S2, Ep8
The Ark Of The Covenant. Josh Gates heads to Israel and Ethiopia to search for the lost Ark of the Covenant, the sacred relic said to contain the Ten Commandments. S3, Ep12
Marsh Madness. The Raneys face a swamp nightmare in Georgia. They must find an ingenious way to reclaim the Buchannans' land from a snake and gator-infested swamp. S4, Ep9
Machine Mayhem. It's the last chance for the Rookies' partnership. Meanwhile, the Cooke brothers fight busted hoses and breakdowns in their quest to strike it rich. S2, Ep6
Against All Odds. Rookie Justin struggles to get his 20-tonne excavator across an extremely busy highway. Plus, Opal Queen Kelly tackles a new challenge with a new partner. S2, Ep7
We Have Not Yet Begun to Fight. As the polar ice descends, The Saga is in danger of sinking, Jake must act fast to save his crew, and Josh gambles big-time by heading towards danger. S11, Ep18
UFOs Over New Mexico. Responding to recent UFO sightings, Josh Gates sends his team to New Mexico for a new investigation into the infamous, unsolved Socorro Landing Incident. S2, Ep8
The Gathering Storm. The team discover tree structures on different sides of the same mountain. As a storm approaches, Bryce prepares to pinpoint Bigfoot's location. S5, Ep7
Marcus and Dale find a huge gold nugget. The Gold Timers uncover their biggest gold haul ever, while Shane and Russell overwork their sluice. S6, Ep14
